<h2>Clearing BW1 Quest</h2>
*Use 2 SS
*The flagship must have lower torpedo stats than the 2nd SS (to ensure mvp is given to 2nd SS)
*Go to 1-1
*Change flagship to another SS if the flagship morale < 40
*Do this until BW1 quest completed
*It usually took about 2-5 Hour(s) playtime (depends on luck) for me to finish this quest.
Please tell me If you have another efficient method. -Thanks-


